  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Average Interfraction Shift of Patients Undergoing Radiotherapy</measure>
    <time_frame>Daily prior to radiation</time_frame>
    <description>Determine the magnitude of the systematic error of patient positioning as determined by cone beam CT (CBCT) and the desired placement based on the treatment planning CT scan.
Every day, prior to radiation treatment, a CBCT will be performed. The CBCT images will be compared to the radiation therapy planning CT image just taken.</description>
